Package: mapcapR
Title: R package for processing and analysis of CAGE data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Vivek", "Bhardwaj", email = "bhardwaj@ie-freiburg.mpg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: mapcapR is a tool for processing and analysis of CAGE data, from raw reads to TSS calling and differential TSS detection
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2)
Imports:
    stats, utils, methods, grDevices,
    plyr, ggplot2,
    BiocParallel, Biostrings, S4Vectors, Rsamtools,
    GenomicAlignments, GenomicRanges, rtracklayer, SummarizedExperiment,
    VariantAnnotation,  Rsubread, limma, edgeR, csaw, CAGEr
biocViews: CAGE, MAPCap
